Tom Quinn (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Quinn_(actor) 0 Thomas Michael Quinn (April 28, 1934, Queens, New York – January 5, 2014, Teaneck, New Jersey) was an American actor who appeared in numerous small roles on television and in various films, including a stint as Detective Patrick Mahon on HBO's The Wire. small roles in the films Major League II and Super 8. He portrayed Coach Bell in The Hammer. Quinn died in 2014 at age 79 from complications of diabetes.
